[cheers and applause]

20:10.667 --> 20:15.267
- Hello, kids.
It's me, Demi Lovato.

20:15.267 --> 20:18.100
all: Mr. Finn?

20:18.100 --> 20:21.900
- I had a nightmare
exactly like this once.

20:21.900 --> 20:24.533
- Guys, Demi's not coming.

20:24.533 --> 20:26.733
Truth is,
I don't know her.

20:26.733 --> 20:28.367
- I know her.
- What?

20:28.367 --> 20:32.500
- I met her at the hotel.
We're breakfast buffet buddies.

20:32.500 --> 20:34.133
- Why didn't you
say anything?

20:34.133 --> 20:36.067
- I didn't want to steal
your thunder,

20:36.067 --> 20:39.367
until I realized
you didn't have any thunder.

20:39.367 --> 20:41.500
- Or the legs
for that dress.

20:43.200 --> 20:45.467
- She said we could get
tickets to her show anytime.

20:45.467 --> 20:47.300
- But tonight's anytime.

20:47.300 --> 20:50.967
- Everybody,
to the van!

20:50.967 --> 20:52.700
Hey.

20:52.700 --> 20:55.367
I hope you learned your lesson,
to always be yourself.

20:55.367 --> 20:56.900
- I have.

20:56.900 --> 21:00.867
But this will make sure
I never forget it.

21:00.867 --> 21:03.367
- That's why I do this.

21:03.367 --> 21:05.133
Oh.

21:05.133 --> 21:07.433
I should have gone
with the waterproof mascara.

21:07.433 --> 21:09.433
[sniffs]

21:09.433 --> 21:11.433
Man up, Dewey.

21:11.433 --> 21:12.467
Let's go.

